_sText:
De_Adrenalin, yes the misspelling is intentional

Basic bomb planting type CS:S map, built for good FPS while playing the map while still offering a bit of detail, being honest though, this map has been in my maps folder for about a year or too and little has changed, although i finally got around to polishing up some areas of the map and making it worthy of being posted on the internet, although I may be improving this map in the future (probably not though unless there are any REAL problems with it) I consider it done, please download and rate, any and all comments are appretiated :) thanks.

+Includes NAV file for bots
-No HDR
